# Monorepo Architecture

Bun workspaces monorepo (`@costly/monorepo`). Three apps, two shared packages.

## Apps

### `apps/api` (`@costly/api`)

Cloudflare Worker ‚Äî the **only** app that talks to the database and external services.

```
apps/api/src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.ts              # fetch handler + scheduled cron
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ exports.ts            # Re-exports AppRouter + shared types for @costly/api-client
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ handlers/             # Business logic + all Drizzle queries
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ middlewares/          # Hono middleware (lib injection, session auth)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ routers/              # Hono HTTP routes
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.ts          # appRouter ‚Üí /api
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ api/v1/           # Versioned resource routers (purchases, ‚Ä¶)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ schema/               # Drizzle tables, relations, Zod schemas
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ utils/                # env, getLib()
```

**Bindings** (via Hyperdrive): configured in `wrangler.jsonc`.

**DB scripts:** `db:up`, `db:down`, `db:generate`, `db:migrate`.

### `apps/frontend` (`frontend`)

Static Vite SPA (TanStack Router + Query + Form). Deployed as a Cloudflare Worker serving `dist/` via the `ASSETS` binding; also wrapped by Tauri iOS.

```
apps/frontend/src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.ts              # Worker entry ‚Äî delegates to ASSETS binding
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ routes/               # File-based TanStack Router pages
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lib/                  # apiClient, purchases API, auth-client, session
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/           # App-specific UI wrappers
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ utils/                # env, formatting helpers
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ styles/tailwind.css   # Tailwind entry
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ router.tsx            # Router factory
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ main.tsx              # Client entry (QueryClientProvider + RouterProvider)
```

**Wrangler:** `assets.directory` ‚Üí `./dist`, SPA fallback via `not_found_handling`.

**Import alias:** `#/*` ‚Üí `./src/*`.

### `apps/mobile` (`@costly/mobile`)

Tauri v2 iOS shell around `apps/frontend/dist`. No Rust business logic ‚Äî WebView loads the shared React UI.

```
apps/mobile/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ package.json          # tauri CLI scripts
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ src-tauri/
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tauri.conf.json   # frontendDist ‚Üí ../frontend/dist
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ gen/apple/        # Xcode project (generated by tauri ios init)
```

## Packages

### `packages/api-client` (`@costly/api-client`)

Automatic type-safe Hono RPC client. **Not codegen** ‚Äî types are inferred at compile time from `AppRouter` exported by `@costly/api`.

```typescript
import { createApiClientWithCredentials } from "@costly/api-client";
const client = createApiClientWithCredentials(apiUrl);
const res = await client.api.v1.purchases.$get({ query: { limit: 20, offset: 0 } });
```

Used by the frontend (and Tauri) for all purchase data. Auth uses `better-auth` client separately.

### `packages/components` (`@costly/components`)

Subframe-generated UI library. Synced from Subframe ‚Äî **do not hand-author components here**.

**Sync:** `cd packages/components && bun sync` (agents do not edit this package ‚Äî see [`.cursor/rules/components-package.mdc`](./components-package.mdc))

**Import in frontend:** `import { Button, TextField } from "@costly/components"`.

